claim.claim-text:
1. A method comprising: 
forming a dielectric on a contact, the contact formed on a substrate; 
forming an opening through the dielectric exposing the contact; 
forming an electrode in the opening, the electrode on the contact; 
forming an adhesive on the dielectric and on the electrode; 
patterning the adhesive exposing a portion of the electrode; 
forming a programmable material on the adhesive and on the electrode; and 
forming a conductor to the programmable material.

4. A apparatus comprising: 
a contact on a substrate; 
a dielectric on the contact, the dielectric having an opening extending to the contact; 
an electrode in the opening, the electrode on the contact; 
an adhesive on the dielectric; 
a programmable material on the adhesive and on the electrode; and 
a conductor to the programmable material.

10. A method comprising: 
forming a dielectric on a contact, the contact formed on a substrate; 
forming an adhesive on the dielectric; 
forming an opening through the adhesive and the dielectric, exposing the contact; 
forming a programmable material on the adhesive and on a first portion of the contact; and 
forming a conductor to the programmable material.

14. A apparatus comprising: 
a dielectric on a contact, the contact on a substrate; 
an adhesive on the dielectric, the adhesive and the dielectric having an opening exposing the contact; 
a programmable material on the adhesive and on a first portion of the contact; and 
a conductor to the programmable material.
